OL,3,COctober is Black History Month, but is
OL,4,Cit time schools taught it all year?
OL,6,FToday (October 1st) marks the start of
OL,7,FBlack History Month, but campaigners
OL,8,Ffor a more inclusive education system
OL,9,Fsay the subject should not just be
OL,10,F'pigeon-holed' into four weeks each
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FThe teaching of black and ethnic-
OL,14,Fminority history is still not a
OL,15,Fmandatory part of the school
OL,16,Fcurriculum.
OL,18,FThat's despite roughly 1 in 5 people
OL,19,Fin the UK identifying as being from a
OL,20,Fnon-white or mixed race background.
