OL,3,COctober is Black History Month, but is
OL,4,Cit time schools taught it all year?
OL,6,FData from multiple exam boards
OL,7,Fanalysed by The Guardian shows that
OL,8,Fjust 1 in 10 GCSE history pupils study
OL,9,Fmodules which mention black peoples'
OL,10,Fcontribution to Britain.
OL,12,FWatch Nick Smith's report ...
OL,14,FLavinya Stennett founded "The Black
OL,15,FCurriculum" which has been campaigning
OL,16,Ffor mandatory inclusion of black
OL,17,Fhistory in all schools since it was
OL,18,Fformed in 2019.
