OL,15,Fthat indicated schools would still
OL,16,Fhave the choice to teach black
OL,17,Fhistory, rather than making it
OL,18,Fmandatory.
OL,20,FFour years on, Lavinya hopes under a
OL,21,Fnew government, things may change:
