OL,3,COctober is Black History Month, but is
OL,4,Cit time schools taught it all year?
OL,6,FHowever, there is one part of the UK
OL,7,Fwhich has already embraced mandatory
OL,8,Finclusion of black and minority ethnic
OL,9,Fhistories and experiences into their
OL,10,Fclassrooms.
OL,12,FIn 2022 the Welsh Government formally
OL,13,Frolled out their Black History
OL,14,FCurriculum, which they claimed would
OL,15,Fmake their children and young people
OL,16,F"more informed citizens".
