OL,4,Cit time schools taught it all year?
OL,6,FTwo years into the new changes, St
OL,7,FPauls' Church School in Cardiff is
OL,8,Frunning a lesson on the black Welshmen
OL,9,Fand women who helped shape their
OL,10,Fmodern nation.
OL,12,FPupils are split into groups and given
OL,13,Finformation on people like former
OL,14,FOlympic athlete Colin Jackson or Dame
OL,15,FShirley Bassey, and told to come up
OL,16,Fwith a pitch as to why they deserve
OL,17,Ftheir own statue.
OL,19,FGemma Maiorano is the school's
OL,20,FEquality, Diversity & Inclusion Lead.
OL,21,FShe said:
