OL,3,COctober is Black History Month, but is
OL,4,Cit time schools taught it all year?
OL,6,FThe Department for Education has made
OL,7,Fno specific commitment to making the
OL,8,Fteaching of black or other ethnic
OL,9,Fminority histories mandatory in
OL,10,Fschools. However, they did say they
OL,11,Fare conducting a review of the current
OL,12,Fcurriculum.
OL,14,FA spokesperson told ITV News:
OL,16,F"The government recently launched an
OL,17,Findependent curriculum and assessment
OL,18,Freview as part of our work to break
OL,19,Fdown the barriers to opportunity for
OL,20,Fevery child, at every stage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
